D-t%C3%B4n-gi%C3%A1o-th%E1%BB%A5-Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh/poem-6ndGhLSrGJ3bYoaJaoWN_Q">Tặng Khổng, Nhan, Mạnh tam thị tử tôn giáo thụ Thái Bình - 贈孔顏孟三氏子孫教授太平</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-t%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-chinh/poem-S-xn8iMkU9i6iXCT585-Ng">Thập ngũ tòng quân chinh - 十五從軍征</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/Th%E1%BB%8D-Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%91%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-s%C6%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%99/poem-YR4ZULh4enTK1LFke3_2aw">Thọ Thẩm đô đốc sơ độ - 壽沈都督初度</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Ti%E1%BA%BFu-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-C4eOy8mqvNSyOkqKQJkQ-A">Tiếu hữu nhân - 誚友人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%C3%A1n/V%C4%83n/poem-ubDVVIoD3ejWyyJRCM9pkQ">Văn - 蚊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-C%C3%A1n/author-Nx2AggB5pgAGcLiAEumXWg">Vũ Cán</a>)<br></div>	</div>
